snippet.title: Alien Holiday - Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Aliens have invaded your town!!
 But there's a citywide, neverending party that you're trying to stop, so that doesn't matter right now.
 Explore the secrets that link these two events together in the comedic turn-based RPG Alien Holiday!

Check out the demo at brunodesn.itch.io/alien-holiday.

And follow us on twitter @alien_holiday for news!
